```proto
message AwardData {
    int32 AwardType = 1;
    int32 Symbol = 2;
    int32 Count = 3;
    int32 Line = 4;
    double Win = 5;
    int32 Multiplier = 6;
}
```

So the issue is that when uk917.proto was authored, the JackpotWin field was missed. This needs to be added to fix the TypeScript compilation errors.

